🌟BIG ANNOUNCEMENT🌟 

I’m so pleased to announce that I’ll be creating a series, the Westgrave Files, for @01firstsecond over the next few years, written and drawn by me. Three middle-grade horror novels (with some good old fashioned coming-of-age shenanigans). Each book can be read as a stand alone, but are linked and will have overlapping characters. Huge thanks to @tetrameter, my wonderful agent, and editor @dezinpub, who acquired these books. You guys made this possible 💚💚💚

Got to draw these guys for a commission (@emmanectric 💚) ; I don’t go here but I still had a lot of fun making these!!
